00:21:14,231 --> 00:21:17,901
Which of you believe
those rumors are true?

268
00:21:17,985 --> 00:21:19,945
What are you doing?

269
00:21:20,487 --> 00:21:22,364
It's okay. Please raise your hand.

270
00:21:22,447 --> 00:21:24,992
If you tell the truth,

271
