356
00:26:34,384 --> 00:26:36,428
Jun-young stabbed his father in the back

357
00:26:37,470 --> 00:26:39,806
to find out who really killed your father.

358
00:26:41,808 --> 00:26:43,059
This is the payback he gets

359
