from his own father...

360
00:26:49,816 --> 00:26:50,984
And mine.

361
00:26:52,319 --> 00:26:53,445
So what?

362
00:26:57,324 --> 00:26:59,492
-Eul.
-What does that have to do with me?

363
00:27:00,076 --> 00:27:01,578
What do you want me to do?

364
